        <field>Remediation_Steps__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Configure Salesforce Data Export to run weekly automated backups of all objects containing ePHI. Document a disaster recovery plan with defined Recovery Time Objectives and Recovery Point Objectives. Test the recovery process at least annually by performing a full data restore to a sandbox environment. Maintain backup logs and recovery test results as evidence for compliance audits.</value>
